{
  "texts": [
    "SayPlan [31] is an embodied agent specifically designed for task planning.",
    "In this agent, the scene graphs and environment feedback serve as the agent's short-term memory, guiding its actions.",
    "CALYPSO [32] is an agent designed for the game Dungeons & Dragons, which can assist Dungeon Masters in the creation and narration of stories.",
    "Its short-term memory is built upon scene descriptions, monster information, and previous summaries.",
    "DEPS [33] is also a game agent, but it is developed for Minecraft."
  ]
}